                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8609" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2161</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1874 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以“数”赋“制”，汇“智”于“质”:北重集团矿用车的三智转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Empower the manufacturing industry with numerical intelligence and integrate numerical intelligence into new quality productivity: Inner Mongolia North Heavy Industry Group Co., Ltd. mine vehicle three wisdom transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张璐，崔鑫鑫，黄荟婕（通讯），张强，赵爽，长青，苑曙光，崔敏杰，王晓燕，于超，郭海全，李来平</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古北方重工业集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智化转型；数智赋能；新质生产力；无人驾驶矿用车；2024百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital intelligence transformation; Number intelligence empowers; New quality productivity; Driverless mining car</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">我国制造业数智化转型需求迫切、数智创新能力不足等问题严重制约制造业转型升级和高质量发展。在技术和市场的双重困境下，内蒙古北方重工业集团有限公司（以下简称“北重集团”）以矿用车的转型升级为切入点，通过数智化手段赋能技术、管理、机制、模式多维度创新，助力“智慧矿车、智慧平台、智慧矿山”为主的“三智建设”朝着“高端化、智能化、国际化”高质量发展，推动新质生产力的涌现。本案例描述了北重集团先后完成无人驾驶矿用车的研发以及对“旧”车进行无人驾驶改造，最终打造无人驾驶矿用车智能化中央控制系统及远程诊断健康服务平台，推进智慧矿山建设的一系列过程。通过案例分析，引导学生理解并掌握数智化转型的动因、要素及实现路径，了解数智化如何赋能新质生产力等，进而为新时期数智赋能传统制造企业转型升级和加强数智化人才培育和储备提供有益范例和理论思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The urgent need for digital intelligence transformation in China&#39;s manufacturing industry and the shortage of digital intelligence innovation ability seriously restrict its transformation and upgrading and high-quality development. Under the dual dilemma of technology and market, Inner Mongolia North Heavy Industry Group Co., LTD. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Beizhong Group&quot;) takes the transformation and upgrading of mining vehicles as the starting point, and enables multi-dimensional innovation of technology, management, mechanism and model through digital intelligent means. Help the &quot;three wisdom construction&quot; based on &quot;smart mining car, smart platform and smart mine&quot; to develop towards &quot;high-end, intelligent and international&quot; high-quality, and promote the emergence of new quality productivity. This case describes a series of processes in which Beizhong Group has completed the research and development of unmanned mining vehicles and the unmanned transformation of &quot;old&quot; vehicles, and finally built an intelligent central control system for unmanned mining vehicles and a remote diagnosis health service platform to promote the construction of smart mines. Through case analysis, students are guided to understand and master the motivation, factors and realization path of digital intelligence transformation, and understand how digital intelligence enables new quality productivity, etc., so as to provide useful examples and theoretical thinking for the transformation and upgrading of traditional manufacturing enterprises with digital intelligence in the new era and strengthen the cultivation and reserve of digital intelligence talents.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智化转型的动因；数智赋能的实现路径；数智化赋能新质生产力；突破式（渐进式）创新；数智变革悖论管理理论；产业融合</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
